snippet.title: Job Simulator Vive Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Vive!

Job Simulator is a tongue-in-cheek virtual reality experience for motion controlled VR platforms. In a world where robots have replaced all human jobs, step into the "Job Simulator" to learn what it was like 'to job'. 

Buy Job Simulator on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/448280/Job_Simulator/

Job Simulator website: https://jobsimulatorgame.com/
